ded for not merging the meshes in the next step\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- do not start the operation!\n\t\t\t\t\t- Mode: optimize\n\t\t\t\t\t- Fuzzy Face Count Target\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- web: high\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- omniverse: highest\n\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t- use my template\n\t\t\t\t- baked workflow - braucht getrennte meshes oder irgendeine material ID\n\t\t\t\t\t- model looks horrible: change to material view\n\t\t\t\t\t- model still looks horrible: change normal map from \"tangent space\" to \"model space\"\n\t\t\t\t\t- Color und Alpha löschen (evtl gar nicht erst mit baken)\n\t\t\t\t\t- purge unused data\n\t\t\t\t\t- pack materials (when having a normal map)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- make paths relative\n\t\t\t\t- optimized mesh workflow\n\t\t\t\t\t- Material\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- Asset Browser\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- Apppend (reuse data)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- delete all the other materials\n\t\t\t\t\t- purge unused data\n\t\t\t- Omniverse\n\t\t\t\t- Mesh ersetzen in .usd file?\n\t\t- Workflow: Provide Assets fast that look better than ever but are not optimized\n\t\t\t- InstaLOD\n\t\t\t\t- Import: Z up\n\t\t\t\t- Mesh Toolkit: Split by Adjaceny\n\t\t\t\t\t- Delete weird cylinders\n\t\t\t\t- *Kleiner Nachtrag: zumindest optimize hätte ich mal drücken können ...*\n\t\t\t\t- UV unwraph: *wird glaube ich automatisch erstellt*\n\t\t\t\t\t- UV pack\n\t\t\t\t- export .fbx\n\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t- Materialien\n\t\t\t\t\t- reduzieren\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- umbennen\n\t\t\t\t\t- verbessern\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- komische Shader ersetzen\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- normal maps löschen\n\t\t\t\t\t- purge\n\t\t\t\t\t- Materialien als Assets speichern\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- /asset library/worl/material library blender\n\t\t\t\t- .blend speichern\n\t\t\t\t\t- Asset Library/work/<robotername>\n\t\t\t- Omniverse\n\t\t\t\t- Rig\n\t\t\t\t- Material\n\t\t\t\t\t- Rougness Maps\n\t\t\t\t\t- Normal Map\n\t\t- Links für das Projekt\n\t\t\t- [Batch Processing](https://instalod.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360014636673-How-to-batch-process-using-InstaLOD-Pipeline)