t\t- [Gltf Confverter](https://.gltf.pmnd.rs) - Link brauche ich\n\t\t\t- threejs\n\t\t\t- codesandbox\n\t\t\t- react drei library\n\t- [[TODO/Asset Library]]\n\t  :LOGBOOK:\n\t  CLOCK: [2024-05-31 Fri 09:36:34]\n\t  :END:\n\t-\n- ### [[Protokoll]]\n  people:: [[Michael Graf]] [[Johannes Baumgärtel]]\n  projekt:: [[MPI]]\n\t- CAD Modell wird angefragt\n\t\t- Spinning Disk nicht von Zeiss\n\t\t- Hamamatsu (?) Kamera nicht von Zeiss\n\t- Feedack an MPI - Zeiss kann seinen Teil beitragen\n\t- Zeiss fragt, ob wir an Kooperationen interssiert sind - what - the - fuck - weil ich ein 3D-Modell angefragt habe. Ich glaubs kaum\n\t\t- Michael Graf fragt unter welchen Bedingungen er das raus geben kann\n\t\t\t- Upscaling\n\t\t\t- Durchsatz\n\t\t\t- Automatisierung\n\t\t- \"Unsere Entwickler sterben auch nicht an langeweile\" - schau mer mal obs klappt mit den Ressoucen\n\t-\n- ### [[Design Sprint]]\n\t- Mit Nina, in Obsidian",536870919]],["^15",[828,"^1A",1721194759668,536870919]],["^15",[828,"^Z","journals/2024_05_30.md",536870919]],["^15",[829,"^K",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[829,"^[",828,536870919]],["^15",[829,"^N",20240530,536870919]],["^15",[829,"^@",true,536870919]],["^15",[829,"^Y","2024-05-30",536870919]],["^15",[829,"^11","2024-05-30",536870919]],["^15",[829,"^B",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[829,"^;","~u66975907-da4b-4495-87d2-3f087c2866d3",536870919]],["^15",[830,"^K",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[830,"^@",false,536870919]],["^15",[830,"^Y","michael graf",536870919]],["^15",[830,"^11","Michael Graf",536870919]],["^15",[830,"^B",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[830,"^;","~u66975907-e4d4-49db-abd9-075a7845ae71",536870919]],["^15",[831,"^K",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[831,"^@",false,536870919]],["^15",[831,"^Y","markus schmidtchen",536870919]],["^15",[831,"^11","Markus Schmidtchen",536870919]],["^15",[831,"^B",1721194759667,536870919]],["^15",[831,"^;","~u66975907-2e1e-47fa-9ab5-85c66d7beffb",536870919]],["^15",[832,"^K",1721194759713,536870919]],