 15:30:14]--[2024-07-23 Tue 15:30:14] =>  00:00:00\n\t\t\t  :END:\n\t\t\t\t- DONE scene raussuchen\n\t\t\t\t  :LOGBOOK:\n\t\t\t\t  CLOCK: [2024-07-23 Tue 15:30:14]--[2024-07-23 Tue 15:30:14] =>  00:00:00\n\t\t\t\t  :END:\n\t\t\t- DONE collider plane\n\t\t\t  :LOGBOOK:\n\t\t\t  CLOCK: [2024-07-23 Tue 16:42:12]--[2024-07-23 Tue 16:42:12] =>  00:00:00\n\t\t\t  :END:\n\t\t\t\t- how?\n\t\t\t- camera attachement\n\t\t\t\t- von Paul abchecken lassen\n\t\t\t- new tool mounting\n\t\t\t\t- tool finden\n\t\t\t- gripper element\n\t\t\t\t- Frank fragen\n\t\t\t- optimieren ganz am Ende - das sieht keiner, das ist nur für die Verteidigung im September nötig, nicht für die Videos\n\t\t\t  collapsed:: true\n\t\t\t\t- als erstes die Pipettespitzen\n\t\t\t\t- beaker\n\t\t\t\t- tisch\n\t\t\t\t- vorgehen\n\t\t\t\t\t- Omniverse\n\t\t\t\t\t  collapsed:: true\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- export usd to Blender\n\t\t\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t\t  collapsed:: true\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- auto uv unwrap\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- bake textures with OV Connector\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- export fbx to InstaLOD\n\t\t\t\t\t- InstaLOD\n\t\t\t\t\t  collapsed:: true\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- optimize\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- remesh\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- export fbx\n\t\t\t\t\t- Blender\n\t\t\t\t\t  collapsed:: true\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- export to usd\n\t\t\t-\n\t\t- Liste mit allen Funktionen für Shyam - Doku\n\t\t- Arbeit Anmelden\n- ### [[Protokoll]]\n  people:: [[Vincent Gerber]] [[Shyam Chanduri]] [[Stephan Weber]]\n  projekt:: [[MPI]]\n  tags:: [[Internal Update]]\n  collapsed:: true\n\t- [[TODO/MPI Doku]]\n\t\t- Iteration\n\t\t\t- remove 'scan image' screen\n\t\t\t- add switch for toggling scan/omniverse window\n\t\t\t\t- when scan went wrong you can check in history\n\t\t\t- start process only when minimal number of objects was found\n\t\t\t- questioning things\n\t\t\t\t- reversed order of the history\n\t\t\t\t- command tab should be a chat-ish with natural language and feedback by the system\n\t\t\t\t\t- the commands shown right now in the command tab should be transferred 